    "description": "Slot Idler is an IDLE game featuring fruitmachines.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEver wanted to know what would happen if you threw a lot of cash into a slotmachine? Here's your chance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSit back, watch the reels spin, hear the sounds and become mesmerized.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- five popular slotmachines, each with different gameplay.<br />\r\n- authentic sounds where possible.<br />\r\n- authentic gameplay behaviour.<br />\r\n- 50 achievements; some require an insane amount of playing and luck.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote:<br />\r\n- The game plays itself, after 25 manual clicks (per machine) you can lock the start-button and sit back.<br />\r\n- There is no way to influence the outcome of the game, it is a slotmachine afterall.<br />\r\n- Game runs in a small fixed size window. No scaling. No full screen. <br />\r\n- Put it in the corner of your desktop while you do something else.<br />\r\n- There is no real money involved.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFuture:<br />\r\n- New machines will be added depending on succes/demand.",
